Introduction

Crush is a South Korean R&B and Hip-Hop Singer and Producer under P Nation. He was one half of the duo Masterpiece.

He officially debuted as a soloist on April 1, 2014, with the single "Sometimes". Prior to his debut, he released two other singles, "Red Dress" and "Crush On You".

He is a member of the project hip-hop group FANXY CHILD.

He is the brother of nov.
